name: Black Angus Beef Choice Boneless Cubed Steak, per lb
description:
Shop for fresh Black Angus Cubed Steak from ALDI. This delicious steak is tenderized to perfection. Cubed steak can be braised, sautéed or pan-fried for a quick and easy meal.

Product Highlights:
Fresh, never frozen 
Hand selected and trimmed
Excellent source of vitamin B12, protein and zinc
Good source of iron, niacin and vitamin B6
 
To avoid cross-contamination and prevent food-borne illnesses, follow these easy steps:

-Wash hands well in hot, soapy water before handling raw meat.
-Keep raw meat and meat juices away from other foods.
-Keep cutting boards separate from other food prep areas and serving platters.

How to store meat
Meat should always be kept cold and placed directly in the refrigerator after purchase.
Our vacuum-sealed packages can be placed directly in the freezer.
Non-vacuum-sealed packages should be wrapped in heavy-duty aluminum foil and labeled prior to freezing.

How to cook the perfect steak
1.  For steaks that are 1-inch thick or greater:  grill or sear for 3 minutes per side for medium-rare, 4 minutes per side for medium.

2. For steaks that are less than 1-inch thick:  grill or sear for 2 minutes per side for medium-rare, 3 minutes per side for medium.

3. Use a meat thermometer to properly cook your steak. Just insert it horizontally into the side of the cut’s center while making sure not to touch any bones or fat.

Medium Rare: 145°
Medium: 160°
Well Done: 170°

4. To avoid releasing the juices of a steak when using a meat thermometer, test for doneness using your hand. With your left hand, palm facing up, touch the tip of your thumb to the tip of your pinky finger.  Using your right index finger, press the muscle at the base of your thumb. This is what well-done feels like. Compare to the feel of your steak.  Touch your thumb to your ring finger for medium-well, middle finger for medium and index finger for rare.

5. Meat continues cooking even when removed from heat.  To achieve desired doneness, all steaks should rest for at least 5 minutes.


When you shop at ALDI, you’ll find that our fresh steaks and roasts are all packed in vacuum-sealed leakproof packaging. This guarantees that your meat will stay fresher, longer. The deep purple color means there’s no air in the package and is an indicator of freshness. Once the package is opened, the meat will turn the bright red you’ve come to expect in high quality beef.

*Not available in California

How to store meat
Meat should always be kept cold and placed directly in the refrigerator after purchase.

description:
ButFirstCoffee, Honey, I'd Rather Bee at the Sea, Some Like it Hatch or You're Cajun me Crazy

ButFirstCoffee
The perfect unique party cheese that is easy to pair, stunning to look at, and the guaranteed eye catcher on any cheeseboard. This cheese is rubbed with real espresso and lavender with notes of butterscotch and caramel. This is a full-bodied cheese with a nutty flavor and smooth texture. This cheese is aged for 6–8 months by master cheesemakers. 

Some Like it Hatch
Made with real New Mexico hatch chiles and coriander, this cheese has mellow lemony undertones and complex smokiness.

Honey I'd Rather Bee at the Sea
Sweet and creamy, this cheese is rubbed with Utah wildflower honey and ancient sea salt. The cheese has a unique pink hew.

You're Cajun Me Crazy:  
This is a cheese for the spice lover who doesn't shy away from cayenne. The rind provides a spectacular punch of heat balanced with the sweet creaminess of the cheddar.  The cheese is rubbed with a blend of garlic, celery seed and cayenne. As the cheese ages, these ingredients infuse the 20-lb. wheel of cheddar with savory notes resembling a delicious wood-fired pizza!

description:
Did you know that there are almost 100 varieties of cucumbers? One of those varieties is the seedless cucumber. Seedless cucumbers are often longer and thinner than regular cucumbers. You'll notice the difference almost immediately as seedless cucumbers are typically wrapped in plastic and don't have a waxy exterior.
Seedless cucumbers even taste different. They're less bitter than regular cucumbers and can even be a bit sweet. The skin is also thinner than normal cucumbers and is edible.

name: Holiday Stocking Stuffer - Puppy Cube Toy
description: Fisher Price® Laugh N Learn® Puppy Activity Cuber - The Laugh & Learn® Puppy’s Activity Cube from Fisher-Price® offers engaging play your baby will love to get their hands on. This retro-inspired activity toy features fun designs, textures, music and lights for toddlers to discover as they twist and turn the blocks. Plus, when little explorers press the buttons on the cube, they’ll hear 25+ songs, sounds and phrases that teach the alphabet, counting 1-10, colors and shapes. Age Grade: 9-36 Mos.

name: Holiday Stocking Stuffer - Phone Toy
description: Fisher Price® Laugh N Learn® 2-in-1 Slide to Learn Smartphone - Swipe up for learning fun with the Laugh & Learn 2-in-1 Slide to Learn Smartphone toy from Fisher-Price. This interactive toy phone looks like the real thing and features your baby’s Laugh & Learn friends, Puppy and Sis, plus two learning modes with “app” and number buttons to press to activate lights, songs and sounds. As toddlers press, slide, and toggle the activities on the pretend phone, they’ll give fine motor skills a good workout while educational songs and phrases introduce them to the numbers and counting, shapes, colors, and more. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 9-36 Mos

name: Monster Truck Tiger Shark with Remote Control
description: Hot Wheels® Monster Trucks 1:24 Scale Tiger Shark RC™ Vehicle - Take the wheel for awesome Monster Trucks action with this remote-control Tiger Shark! This untamed predator of the Monster Trucks universe can plow through various obstacles with its Terrain Action Tires™ and all-wheel-drive capabilities. Launch into a "Shark Tooth Chomp" as it smashes and crashes into anything in its path. Monster Truck fans will want it and the Hot Wheels® RC Monster Trucks Race Ace™ and HW 5-Alarm™ to wage epic battle sequences just like those in Monster Trucks Live. Each sold separately, subject to availability. Colors and decorations may vary. Agre Grade: 4Y+

name: Holiday Stocking Stuffer - Coffee Cup Toy
description: Fisher Price® Laugh N Learn® Wake Up N Learn® Coffee Mug - Baby can start playtime with a fresh brew of their own with the Laugh & Learn Wake Up & Learn Coffee Mug from Fisher-Price. Featuring colorful lights, 20+ songs and phrases, and fun hands-on activities to explore, this interactive learning toy styled like a to-go beverage cup is filled to the brim with engaging play for babies and toddlers. Requires 3 AG13 (LR44) Button Cell batteries, included. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 6-36 Mos

name: Holiday Stocking Stuffer - Lil Gamer Toy
description: Fisher Price® Laugh N Learn® Lil Gamer - The Laugh & Learn Lil’ Gamer toy from Fisher-Price helps keep your mini-me busy with engaging hands-on learning play. It looks like a grownup video game with a D-pad, A and B buttons and a light-up screen, but it’s sized just right for small hands to press & explore. As babies and toddlers play, educational songs and phrases introduce directions, colors, numbers and shapes. Requires 3 AAA batteries (R03) included. Age Grade: 6-36 Mos

name: Monster Truck Rhinomite with Remote Control
description: Hot Wheels® Monster Trucks 1:24 Scale Rhinomite™ RC Vehicle - Take the wheel for awesome Monster Trucks action with a remote-control Hot Wheels Monster Trucks Rhinomite! It's 1:24 scale and features authentic details of the Rhinomite character including its massive rhino horn. Plow through obstacles with its Grip Action Tires and discover the endless crashing and smashing possibilities. name: Barbie Play Doh - Hearts & Heir

name: Phase 10 Card Game
description: PHASE 10 Card Game - From the makers of UNO™ comes a rummy-type card game with a challenging and exciting twist! The object of the game is to be the first player to complete 10 varied phases with two sets of three, one run of seven, or seven cards with the same color. The twist is that each Phase to be completed is specific for each hand dealt. Players who complete one Phase advance to the next, but those who don't must keep trying until they do. Each deck features “Wild” and Skip” cards, which add excitement and can help you get out of a sticky situation. A “Wild” card can be used in place of a number card, as well as be used as any color to complete any phase, while a “Skip” card causes your opponent to lose a turn! Be the first person to complete all ten phases to win the game. Includes 108 cards and instructions. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 7Y+

name: UNO All Wild Card Game
description: UNO All Wild™ - In UNO All Wild™ card game, every single card is wild for a fast-paced, even more unpredictable version of this family favorite! There's no matching of number or color like regular UNO®, but it's not as easy as it sounds. Special Action Cards really change the game! There's a Wild Skip Two card where players skip two other players instead of the traditional one, a Wild Forced Swap card where players change entire hands and more! This edition is as addictive as it is exhilarating and makes a great gift for players 7 years and older. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 7Y+

name: UNO Card Game
description: UNO® Card Game - UNO™ is the classic and beloved card game that’s easy to pick up and impossible to put down! Players take turns matching a card in their hand with the current card shown on top of the deck either by color or number. Special action cards deliver game-changing moments as they each perform a function to help you defeat your opponents. These include Skips, Reverses, Draw Twos, color-changing Wild and Draw Four Wild cards. You’ll find 25 of each color (red, green, blue, and yellow), plus the eight Wild cards, inside the 108-card deck. If you can’t make a match, you must draw from the central pile! And when you’re down to one card, don’t forget to shout “UNO!” The first player to rid themselves of all the cards in their hand before their opponents wins. It’s Fast Fun for Everyone!™ Includes 108 cards and instructions. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 7y+

name: UNO Teams Card Game
description: UNO Teams™ - UNO Teams is a new way to play the classic game! Players still match color, number and symbol but instead of every-man-for-himself, they team up in pairs of two and play together to win. Special cards and rules help teammates work together, but both players must get rid of all the cards in their hands to win. And remember, when you (or your partner!) are down to your last card, don't forget to yell "UNO!" Age Grade: 7Y+

name: UNO Spiderman or Lord of the Rings Theme Card Game
description: UNO® Card Game - UNO™ is the classic and beloved card game that’s easy to pick up and impossible to put down! Players take turns matching a card in their hand with the current card shown on top of the deck either by color or number. Special action cards deliver game-changing moments as they each perform a function to help you defeat your opponents. These include Skips, Reverses, Draw Twos, color-changing Wild and Draw Four Wild cards. You’ll find 25 of each color (red, green, blue, and yellow), plus the eight Wild cards, inside the 108-card deck. If you can’t make a match, you must draw from the central pile! And when you’re down to one card, don’t forget to shout “UNO!” The first player to rid themselves of all the cards in their hand before their opponents wins. It’s Fast Fun for Everyone!™ Includes 108 cards and instructions. Colors and decorations may vary. Age Grade: 7y+

name: Mini Rubik's Cube Toy
description:
World’s Smallest Rubik’s Cube
The world’s top-selling 3-Dimensional puzzle is now available in the world’s smallest size! Twist and turn the cube using various combinations to return it to its original state, one solid color on every side.
Ages 8+

name: Mini Barbie Doll Toy
description:
World’s Smallest Barbie Figures, 2 Assorted Styles
Introducing the World’s Smallest 1959 Barbie, dressed in her classic swimsuit! Dive into nostalgia with this adorable miniature replica of the iconic fashion doll that has enchanted generations.
Standing at a mere 2.75 inches tall, this pint-sized Barbie captures all the glamour and style of the original, complete with her timeless swimsuit attire and removable sunglasses. 
Whether you’re a seasoned collector or simply looking to add a touch of retro charm to your collection, the World’s Smallest Barbie is sure to delight. 
The perfect Easter basket stuffer, stocking stuffer, and party favor for the collectors in your life, and more! 
For Barbie fans of all ages. Recommended for ages 6 and up

name: Mini Etch-a-Sketch
description:
World’s Smallest Etch-A-Sketch
Twist your way to exciting pictures with the world’s smallest Etch A Sketch! It works just like the classic Etch A Sketch, powered by skill and imagination!
Ages 3+

name: Mini Stretch Armstrong
description:
World’s Smallest Stretch Armstrong
The world’s original S-t-r-e-t-c-h muscle man is back! The smallest Stretch EVER, pull and twist his arms, legs and torso. Stretch stretches nearly four times his size and then returns back to his original shape. He may be the most irresistible miniature ever!  Ages 6+

name: Mini Hot Wheels Car Toy
description:
World’s Smallest Hot Wheels Series 9
GET READY TO REV YOUR ENGINES: World’s Smallest Hot Wheels are back with Series 10! This wave adds three iconic racers to the lineup: Buzz Off, Ramblin Wrecker, and Sooo Fast! Each sold separately.
AUTHENTIC MINIATURE DESIGN: Tiny but tough! These officially licensed replicas feature real die-cast metal and working wheels—small enough to park on a quarter.
COMES COMPLETE WITH: Each car comes with a mini version of the original Hot Wheels blister card—perfect for display or safekeeping.
PERFECT FOR EASTER, PARTIES, AND STOCKINGS: A fun-sized surprise for any occasion—Easter, birthdays, stockings, or just because!
A COLLECTIBLE MUST HAVE: A fantastic addition to any Hot Wheels collection. For fans of all ages. Recommended for ages 8 and up.

name: Mini Elf-on-a-shelf Toy
description:
World’s Smallest the Elf on the Shelf
Ages 6+
The World’s Smallest Elf on the Shelf is a timeless Christmas classic!  A miniature replica of the original full-sized Elf on the Shelf, World’s Smallest is less than 4 inches from the tip of his hat to the bottom of his feet and is fully articulated.  It’s the perfect Christmas collectible toy and stocking stuffer!

How to select pomegranates:
Pomegranates should have a deep red color.
It should be hard on the outside.
It should feel heavy for its size.
Pomegranates should not be bruised or cracked.

Tomato Tips:
Be sure to keep tomatoes out of the refrigerator unless they are sliced. The refrigeration diminishes the tomato’s flavor.
Make tomatoes easier to peel by putting them in boiling water for about 30 seconds and then letting them cool. You can then remove the peels with a sharp knife. Or, if you don’t want to wait for the tomatoes to cool, you can plunge them into cool water for easy peeling.

How to Pick Tomatoes:

Pick tomatoes with bright, shiny skin and firm flesh.

•Pick tomatoes with bright, shiny skin and firm flesh.
